---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Simple, Honest Pricing | Astrobot.design"
  description="Transparent pricing for web design, pre-built websites, and headless CMS solutions. No hidden fees."
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb Navigation -->
  <nav class="py-4 border-b border-border/40">
    <div class="container text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <a href="/pricing" class="text-foreground font-medium">Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Simple, Honest Pricing</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
          No hidden fees. No surprises. Choose the service that fits your business needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="p-8 bg-background rounded-lg border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">Websites for Sale</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Pre-built templates</p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">$599<span class="text-lg text-muted-foreground"> - $1,299</span></p>
          
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">What's Included:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Professional template</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Customization & setup</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">1 year hosting included</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">3-5 day launch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">SEO optimized</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <a href="/websites-for-sale" class="block w-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-center">
            Browse Websites
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-background rounded-lg border border-2 border-primary relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
            Most Popular
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">Web Design (Orbit)</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Custom 5-page site</p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">$1,500</p>
          
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">What's Included:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">5 custom pages</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Mobile responsive</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">SEO optimized</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">1 week launch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Maintenance included</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="block w-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-center">
            Book Consultation
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-background rounded-lg border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">Web Design (Supernova)</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Custom unlimited pages</p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">$3,500</p>
          
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">What's Included:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Unlimited pages</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Blog integration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Advanced SEO</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">3 week launch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Ongoing support</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="block w-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-center">
            Book Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-muted/30 rounded-lg border border-border max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Headless CMS Add-on</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Power up any of our web design packages with a headless CMS. Manage your content independently without touching code.
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Starting at $500/month</p>
        <a href="/headless-cms" class="inline-block text-primary hover:text-primary/80 font-medium">
          Learn More →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Feature Comparison</h2>
      
      <div class="overflow-x-auto max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-bold">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 px-4 font-bold">Websites<br/>for Sale</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 px-4 font-bold">Orbit<br/>(5 pages)</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 px-4 font-bold">Supernova<br/>(Unlimited)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Price</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">$599-1,299</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">$1,500</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">$3,500</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border bg-muted/20">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Design</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Template</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Custom</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Custom</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Pages</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">5-10</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">5</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Unlimited</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border bg-muted/20">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Blog</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Add-on</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Add-on</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Mobile Responsive</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border bg-muted/20">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">SEO Optimized</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Hosting (Year 1)</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Included</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Included</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border bg-muted/20">
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Turnaround Time</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">3-5 days</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">1 week</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">3 weeks</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Support</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Email</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Email</td>
              <td class="text-center py-3 px-4">Priority</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">What's included in the first year of hosting?</summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">All packages include domain, hosting, SSL certificate, and email setup for the first year. After the first year, hosting continues at $99/year.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">Can I upgrade or change my plan?</summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">Yes! You can upgrade from Websites for Sale to custom design, or from Orbit to Supernova. We'll handle the transition smoothly.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">Do you offer payment plans?</summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">For larger projects, we offer flexible payment options. Contact us to discuss a custom arrangement.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">What happens if I need changes after launch?</summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">We offer hourly support rates for post-launch changes and updates. Rates vary based on complexity.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">Do you offer a refund guarantee?</summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">We're confident in our work, but if you're not satisfied within 30 days, we'll discuss options with you.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Choose your service above or book a free consultation to discuss your project.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
            Web Design
          </a>
          <a href="/websites-for-sale" class="border border-border px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-muted transition-colors">
            Websites for Sale
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
